<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7395> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7395" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Monetalis. In MRR 2.252, and Index, 617, refer also to Crawford, RRC 1.327, no. 325, 101 B.C. Pr., uncertain date; probably between 93 and 89. In MRR 2.465, add ILLRP 485. See Syme, above, on no. 3; Wiseman, NM 260, no. 388. In 80 B.C. he is listed first among witnesses in a fragment  of an SC from Cormi in Lycia (TAM 2.3.899).\n" .
